defs.name: HEIGHT
defs.docs: Height is a static variable. Height maximum space for Bob Family. Bob Family have 6 children, 1 wife  1 himself. Height of Bob Family or Family space will be 8. In Height parents are also include while depth parents are excluded.

defs.name: DEPTH
defs.docs: Another static variable is Depth. Depth is level pointer. Means If a node name with (Bob) and alice asked how much members in your family. Bob will answer like I have 1 son and a daughter and both have 2 sons and 2 daughters. My  family size will be 6.

defs.name: Results
defs.docs:

  otherwise program is in other state.
